Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I will make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NEven if it means hurting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it means hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Because deep down,\NI know our wishes are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA, IONA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] But you know\Nthat too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NSo why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:05.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU]\NMy head is killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Tea and pickled plums\Ndo wonders for hangovers, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU sighs]\NYou're the best, Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hope we're not being\Ntoo loud for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU]\NShut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NOh, Ru, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You oughta get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's cool--I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going out\Nto meet with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU]\NWugh--Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NHave fun. And be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,\Nwhat's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Your big brother's just here\Nto see you off, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, weirdo! I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NSee you later, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What happens when\Nthe last space is filled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NIt's all couples here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should meet up\Nat a different spot next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhat, are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect place\Nfor single girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Some hot guy might pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean that do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou realize that's a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, did someone\Nask you out here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, y-yeah, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NReally? Was he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you go on a date?\NWas it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Changing the subject!\NLet's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me\Nabout this guy?! Was he nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] It's really not worth\Ntalking about, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NAw... No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI wanna know! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm... Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps, squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI hums]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIt's all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,For this price,\Nit's hard to say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh-huh! And they're\Ntotally our style!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet Grandma would like these!\NI'll get her one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. Ru's really\Nhaving fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I was thinking\NI'd buy you some scrunchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So you can match the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NSounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NRuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Come look! Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NIt's nice and quiet over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me sit down for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE] Say cheese!\N--[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha, I couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That, and my friends in\NAomori asked for a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NA picture of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been texting back\Nand forth and I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,you were really cool,\Nso they wanted to see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,what you look like.\NOh, and this them, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHey! Show me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasted so much time\Nwishing I had friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've realized you guys\Nwere here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should finally\Nget a cell phone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThat came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, I've been thinking\Nabout it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What if, like, something happens\Nand I need to call Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Or someone moves away\Nand I want to keep in touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Could I look at yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll go phone\Nshopping next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NBut I dunno, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're gonna\Nbe able to figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh? Are they that complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, super hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] We'll have to\Ngive her special training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NNo matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,...even if I go far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,One more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't get a cell phone\Nunless you go to Akihabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I've seen them\Nfor sale all over town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSure, you can buy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but if you don't activate\Nthem in Akihabara,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,they'll never work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat?! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] ...I won't lose\Nanyone, ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NDon't be such a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki's just messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NYou really had me going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Shows what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI laughs] Maybe a\Nlittle training wouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm getting thirsty.\NLet's find something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\N'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIce cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thought she said\Nshe was thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NThis looks good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NNo, it doesn't! Look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a reason\Nnobody's buying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's winter! It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[wind chimes ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,--[bells ringing]\N--[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[bells ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NOne small caramel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NRuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[WALLA: CROWD]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NWhat was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHitoe. Can we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, is this a--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NWIXOSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NOpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Geez,\Nthey're holding tournaments
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,everywhere these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Are there Selectors... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NNo, but let's still go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWait. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,There's... one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit, it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NSelectors! I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's battle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIt's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,So you were... following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. My pal could stand\Nto work on her manners, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, Eldora!\NI just knew they'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The heavens have parted\Nand Selectors have descended!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no mere coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,This is destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Seeing as they're\Nholding a tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,it would be kinda weird\Nif they didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Alas, though I try to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.73,Main,,0,0,0,,it seems that battles\Nare drawn to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYeah, you try real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Like when you came here\Nlooking for someone to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Poo! Can't you play\Nalong for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NSorry again, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I think she was dropped on\Nher head as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI snarls]\NAnyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI grunts]\NCan we battle pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NA back alley! [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NOut of curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,you went to the big Iona\Nfan event thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we wanted\Nto go pretty bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.99,Main,,0,0,0,,but it just didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Cryin' shame, don't ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[WORKERS]\NHuh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,--[WORKER A] Are you lost?\N--Wait.... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[WORKER B]\NUmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Omigosh, she is so\Nlousy with directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,we spent half the day bursting\Ninto every other building
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,in town, running\Naround and around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Then-- [yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Shush! Shush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NI surrender! Mercy! Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Please ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,We've all faced\Ntragedies in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but our tears\Nshall become starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,and our wishes shooting stars\Nin the field of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWait. Um. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NNo battles. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It just is not worth\Nthe risk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NOh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're Selectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That means your wish'll\Nnever come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happens if\Nyou lose? It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NHeavens! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I hadn't heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,After your seventh\Nloss, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,The magical WIXOSS factors\Ninside you go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it's like-- Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,--And your guts go-- Pchoo!\N--You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] What really happens to\Nyou is even worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You lose all of your rights\Nas a Selector. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] As for your wish,\Nit becomes corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,For example, let's say your\Nwish was to become wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,After losing three battles, not\Nonly would that wish fail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,to come true, you would\Nplummet into poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish was to be\Nan expert pianist,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't just\Nlose your piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Something would happen\Nthat would prevent you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,from playing ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Something to ensure your wish\Ncould never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,All I can tell you is\Nher wish was to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You can imagine what a\Ncorruption of that would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A corrupted wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That means... a new plot twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I know I'm a Selector,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but I was able to make my wish\Ncome true without WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's way cooler to\Ndo it with magic and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not nearly that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I won plenty of battles and it\Nonly brought me more misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you win\Nagain and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,your LRIG has to\Nagree to your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And even then, the cost of\Nbecoming an Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO]\NAre you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The oath. Do you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,"The laws of the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept the laws\Nof the Selector".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\N"And upon this sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NI know all that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right here in chapter two,\N"How an LRIG is born," see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Flames of Void Play\Nthe Victory Song of Oblivion"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,is the book, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.29,Main,,0,0,0,,A hundred percent awesome\Nand a hundred percent true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's just a novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe. Would you\Nshow me to her, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHi, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We've met before. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NOh! Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You totally felt familiar to me,\Nbut I couldn't figure out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chiyori,\Nuse that noggin of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYour first battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the girl who beat you?\NHow could you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a card now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NAfter my wish was granted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I took the place of my LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Wow, you don't\Nsay! You too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] You get it now?\NThis is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't go to school anymore or\Neat ice cream with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Or be with the one I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you earned your wish, I\Ncan't let you turn into an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nhow many times you win,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll just end up like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NHuh? Oh yeah, um, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] If you're an LRIG,\Nyou know about Mayu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.65,Main,,0,0,0,,and the white room\Nand all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,If you've suffered\Nthrough this yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,how can you subject\Nsomeone else to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Well, my memory HAS\Nbeen awfully spotty lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's how things work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like this is\Nfinally sinking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So now that you know,\Nyou won't battle anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NSweet! It's just like the novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The heroine becomes\Nthe card in the final chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,and it slaps you with a big, fat\N"to be continued" at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,That's even better than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,If I get a wish and I get to\Nenter the world of WIXOSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,that's like a,\Nlike a double wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI grunts]\NChiyorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyorumba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I need a cool LRIG name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You've done this before.\NWhat's your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] I wouldn't worry\Nabout it if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWait, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,it's like you don't think\NI can win at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NNo, I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the best ever. All your\Nlosses are just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWhy're you such a hater?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NRu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NListen to me, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhat's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NThat's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:19.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Come back! Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I'll fight,\Nand I'll win the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, it'll all be over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NUse White Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NBut why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko won, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NRuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA, URITH]\NAnd upon this sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhy the long face, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWe're partners, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama. Why did--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]\NTama! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NDid you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Urith explained it.\NWeren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] She said Iona won\Nmore than enough battles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,to have her wish granted,\Nbut for whatever reason
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,the time wasn't right\Nand she needed to wait
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,for something else\Nto happen first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSo whatever the condition was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,it was met in this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NIona, what was your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Hmph. To become\Nan LRIG, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] But I had to be the\NLRIG of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,stronger than me,\Nso we could keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So your condition wasn't to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,but to lose to\Nthe right Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] And what\Nhappens to Ruko's wish
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're her LRIG, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:35.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Then we'll work out\Nthe details ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Ru.\NI knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... What happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWho knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]\NNo... Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhy did you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You should've accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to see Tama, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There's there only one way\Nfor that wish to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Not like that! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Then why do you\Nstill carry me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] If you're "done,"\Nyou should throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I was right. You want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYou can't give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NI wasn't going to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring her\Nwith you? For her sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Or did you want to\Nbattle after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NIt's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't know what\Nmight happen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NNo kidding! Tama disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona became your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could've\Npredicted any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's to say it\Nwon't get even worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But I have to see Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,And I... I still want to\Nhelp you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. We agreed on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I know we did,\Nbut everything's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all as confused\Nabout this as you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,but we'll work it out\Ntogether, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] You don't have to\Nshoulder the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,by yourself. You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We're friends.\NWe can all help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHitoe... Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] There are too many\Nthings I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What is Ruko trying\Nto accomplish with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that we're the same. I\Nknow that she longs for battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But that wish of hers\Nis a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I still want to help you\Nand everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NAn LRIG only accepts a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,that they know they can grant.\NWe aren't omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, they held onto\Nthat vague impossibility
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,to the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise things went\Nas poorly as they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NBut I'm her LRIG now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Things are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to change her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI won't let her waste her time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,chasing after some\Nimpossible wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I want her to battle\Nto her heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,To love it and long for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWith me at her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANNOUNCER]\NNext stop: Shinjuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my only clue\Nto finding Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Nothing.\NJust talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWait for me, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NAkira! She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] The next one of you\Npunks who says that name
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,in front of me is gonna get\Ntheir teeth kicked in, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NWould you shut the hell up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIf she doesn't have Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NMastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"That Feverish Bond."
